OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F432A1775124136
OL,3,CRising fuel costs cancel flights
OL,4,Cbetween London and Cornwall
OL,6,FThe service has been operated by
OL,7,FCornwall's Skybus since the previous
OL,8,Foperator, Eastern Airways, went bust
OL,9,Flast November. An agreement with
OL,10,FSkybus was due to end on 31 May, but
OL,11,F"economic uncertainty" has halted
OL,12,Fthings earlier than expected.
OL,14,FCustomers have been told they'll get a
OL,15,Ffull refund.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/6
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,433,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F432A1775124136
OL,3,CRising fuel costs cancel flights
OL,4,Cbetween London and Cornwall
OL,6,FSkybus managing director Jonathan
OL,7,FHinkles said: "The huge rise in the
OL,8,Fglobal cost of fuel following the
OL,9,Fconflict in the Gulf, coupled with a
OL,10,Fsignificant drop in new passenger
OL,11,Fbookings since mid-February's
OL,12,Fannouncement of the planned closure of
OL,13,Fthe PSO air route, forms an
OL,14,Finsurmountable barrier to the service
OL,15,Fcontinuing through April and May.
OL,26,@oD@OOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/6
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
