OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,433,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F432A1775124136
OL,3,CRising fuel costs cancel flights
OL,4,Cbetween London and Cornwall
OL,6,F"At a time of great economic
OL,7,Funcertainty and steps being taken to
OL,8,Fconserve energy worldwide, it is
OL,9,Fneither environmentally nor
OL,10,Feconomically sound for us to continue
OL,11,Fflying with vastly reduced passenger
OL,12,Fnumbers.
OL,14,F"We would like to extend our sincere
OL,15,Fthanks to all those who have supported
OL,16,Fus ` whether as passengers, as local
OL,17,Fstakeholders or as team members
OL,18,Fdelivering service to our customers `
OL,19,Fthrough our recent months of Cornwall-
OL,20,FLondon air service provision."
OL,26,@nD@AOUvD@AOU|D@^O]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/6
