CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F432A1775124136
OL,3,CRising fuel costs cancel flights
OL,4,Cbetween London and Cornwall
OL,6,FIn an earlier statement, Skybus said:
OL,7,F"In view of circumstances beyond our
OL,8,Fcontrol, Skybus has advised Cornwall
OL,9,FCouncil that services will now cease
OL,10,Fat an earlier date. The final services
OL,11,Fin each direction will take place on
OL,12,FThursday, 2 April 2026.
OL,14,F"We are therefore contacting all
OL,15,Fcustomers with bookings throughout
OL,16,FApril and May to advise that flights
OL,17,Fwill no longer take place as planned."
OL,26,@vD@AOUyD@fO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/6
