FL,433,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43206
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F432A1775124136
OL,3,CRising fuel costs cancel flights
OL,4,Cbetween London and Cornwall
OL,6,FSome disappointed passengers have said
OL,7,Fthe cancellations now mean a six-hour
OL,8,Ftrain journey, and additional time off
OL,9,Fwork.
OL,11,FCornwall's Skybus has had previous
OL,12,Fissues with finding suitably sized
OL,13,Faircraft for the route and saw a 20
OL,14,Fper cent seat occupancy.
OL,16,FCornwall Council is now favouring
OL,17,Fseeking a commercial link, preferably
OL,18,Fto London City airport.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/6
